glib2.0 (2.16.2-1) unstable; urgency=low

  [ Loic Minier ]
  * Drop nautilus conflicts as it triggers a bug in the APT resolver on
    dist-upgrade.
  * Update patch 01_gettext-desktopfiles with a newer version taken from the
    Ubuntu package.
